l_meta":{"origin":33850,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Allah teaches Adam greeting of peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah created Adam in His image, sixty cubits tall. When He created him, Allah said: Go and greet these groups of assembled angels with peace and listen to how they greet you, for this will be the greeting\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17993,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/02\/02\/bad-smell-offends-angels\/","url_meta":{"origin":33850,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Angels: Whatever offends people also offends angels","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 2, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever eats onions, garlic, or leeks should not approach our mosque, for the angels are offended by whatever offends the children of Adam.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 564 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39736,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/17\/angels-speak-tongues\/","url_meta":{"origin":33850,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Angels: Truth spoken by angels on tongues of people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 17, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has angels who speak upon the tongues of the children of Adam about whether a man was good or evil.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 9318 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35540,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/04\/jisr-jahannam\/","url_meta":{"origin":33850,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sirat: The Prophets pass over the bridge of Hell","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 4, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI will be the first to cross the bridge over Hell. The supplication of the Messengers on that day will be: O Allah, keep us safe! O Allah, keep us safe! There will be hooks on the sides\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3372,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/06\/12\/all-created-from-adam\/","url_meta":{"origin":33850,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Humanity: Allah created all people from Adam","author":"Ab